The specification we would like to verify are detailed in binary_search.h
Just compile the file with your favorite C compiler and execute the output.

This output should contain a trace looking as:

=====
searching index of 10101 (expecting 5050): 5050

searching index of 10101 (expecting -1): -1

ERROR FOUND (invalid array length)
searching index of LEN (error previously reported): 50

ERROR FOUND (unsorted array)
searching index of 101 (error previously reported): -1
=====
